Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Now possible to batch threads (only display a given number of threads per
  page)
- Allow discussion metadata attribute can now be set to true for a given
  portal type (it is no longer necessary to manually activate comments for each
  document)
- Now possible to subscribe to 2 kinds of events: post creation (mainly for
  moderators), and post publication (for people who want to know when new posts
  get publically available on a forum)

Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
-
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Comment forums are no longer created at comment authorization time, but when
  the first comment is posted
  
